            </div>
            <div class="panel-body">
			The long-term goal of this project is to develop a cost-effective and user friendly monitoring system for data collection on air quality in urban areas.  Public officials as well as citizens can collect air quality data first-hand and use it to determine if there is a public health concern due to air quality. If there is, citizens and policymakers can explore potential policy options for helping to reduce the problem.</div>
